GSD.description:
EDAC/highbank: Fix memory leak in highbank_mc_probe()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.1.9 by commit b7863ef8a8f0fee96b4eb41211f4918c0e047253, it was introduced in version v3.6 by commit a1b01edb274518c7da6d69b84e7558c092282aad. For more details please see the references link.
